Terra Firma in Talks on $1.9 Billion Theater Chain Sale, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-12T01:35:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/terra-firma-in-talks-on-1-9-billion-theater-chain-sale-ft-says.html
Terra Firma Capital Partners Ltd.,
the private equity firm run by  Guy Hands , has begun exclusive
discussions with BC Partners Holdings Ltd. and Omers Private
Equity Inc. to sell the Odeon & UCI Cinemas Group Ltd. chain for
1.2 billion pounds ($1.9 billion), the Financial Times reported,
without saying where it got the information. Hands is expected
to hire Bank of America Merrill Lynch to run the auction, the FT
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 